                                                Symptoms: <%= ord.symptoms %>

                                            </p>
                                            <p class="card-text">
                                                Booked on: <%= ord.date %>

                                            </p>
                                            <p class="card-text"><b>
                                                    Fee: Rs.<%=ord.fee%>
                                                </b></p>

